{"tid":1335553,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【7.21有人冒警】和理非對偽警說不！","createTime":"2019-07-20T14:33:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T05:07:57.000Z","uid":238051,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e67c4ecb45b77c3b7723b61743d697cd7cf314a7","tid":1335553,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T14:33:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">承上一個post：</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">【有人冒警】面對冒警情境練習場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1332100\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1332100</a></span><br />\n<br />\n今次要團結所有抗爭者<br />\n進行<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>和理非式打倒冒警人士</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n眾所週知警方近日不停打壓和平示威<br />\n而且今日於荃灣發現炸蛋<br />\n加上兩次撐警集會<br />\n令警方士氣更盛<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>冒警人士好大機會於7.21遊行搞事！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地要做嘅事非常簡單<br />\n就係要一齊履行良好市民嘅責任<br />\n每次見到冇佩戴委任證的疑似冒警人士<br />\n同隔離左右手足一齊清楚指出懷疑冒警行為<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">直至冒警人士被警察拘捕或帶離現場！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n留意7.21<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不要自行逮捕冒警人士</span></strong></span><br />\n亦千祈<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>唔好郁手攻擊疑似偽警！</strong></span></span><br />\n首先因為明天會有好多老弱婦孺在附近<br />\n偽警通常幾人同時行動，而且持有攻擊性武器<br />\n唔好令旁人受傷<br />\n其次因為自行逮捕會有相當風險<br />\n<br />\n我地7.21對偽警行為的首要目的係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">令更多人注意到冒警問題</span></strong></span><br />\n尤其係附近嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">記者朋友</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n請保持隊形，跟住講：<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警\n你扮警察\n冇委任證\n涉嫌傷人\n藏有攻擊性武器</code></pre><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>保障同行手足<br />\n向偽警說不！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />\n有用連結：<br />\n【我冇嘢講2.0】有人冒警！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1319116\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1319116</a><br />\n<br />\n你涉嫌冒警及嚴重傷害他人身體，我而家要行使《刑事訴訟程序條例》第101條第2項將你拘捕<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1317207\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1317207</a></span>[/"},{"pid":"8ab28181874b60ca8d50ce00df800e44c65c960e","tid":1335553,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T14:34:10.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警\n你扮警察\n冇委任證\n涉嫌傷人\n藏有攻擊性武器</code></pre>"},{"pid":"afa9c7bfd0511ba5fdb86d2c47a431164c38f7a6","tid":1335553,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T14:45:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fb54d41010affab60e22e24e04981fc1bd153860","tid":1335553,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T14:51:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8e75df49be74452b83842f360437dcae1c3563c7","tid":1335553,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T15:01:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea412d65507c60b4c2f9b6d214bae87a21e79848","tid":1335553,"uid":36489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T15:02:15.000Z","msg":"721 見！"},{"pid":"10800da899b562788e943faa0e772297d9e58443","tid":1335553,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea412d65507c60b4c2f9b6d214bae87a21e79848","tid":1335553,"uid":36489,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T15:02:15.000Z","msg":"721 見！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T15:03:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d401ef98007a406ddb21016a54a2b5eb964ac28","tid":1335553,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T15:07:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e3313c7743e2623644689e5d0ceb8014feb1793","tid":1335553,"uid":34916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T15:49:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9edbcb4a2be72b52a7ddca1798b636e5445de4c6","ti